#'~> 0.3.1' is satisfied by 0.3.1, 0.3.2, 0.3.3, etc.
#'~> 0.3.1' is not satisfied by 0.3.0
#'~> 0.3' is satisfied by 0.3.1, 0.4.0, 0.5.1, etc.
#'~> 0.3' is not satisfied by 0.2.0, 0.2.1, etc.

